						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in the Siddhēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 12th Century.</p>						

						<p>This record seems to belong to a Chālukya king whose <hi rend="italic">pras11asti</hi> is cited in the earlier lines. The rest of the epigraph is damaged and worn out except for the concluding portion bearing the imprecation. </p>						

